# Attach conntrack application helpers to their control channels, mirroring the reference
# config's helper intent abstractly. FTP is narrowed to an RFC 5737 host (so it scopes to
# IPv4); TFTP is left dual-stack; PPTP is IPv4-only by its kernel helper. Documentation ranges
# only (RFC 5737).
#ACTION            SOURCE   DEST                 PROTO   DPORT
CT:helper:ftp      net      loc:198.51.100.10    tcp     21
CT:helper:tftp     net      loc
CT:helper:pptp     net      loc
